', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/180312/', '', 'Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Anifrolumab, Ravulizumab, Diroximel fumarate, Abatacept, Upadacitinib, Apremilast, Inebilizumab, Cladribine, Belumosudil, Belimumab, More', 'Propranolol, Metoprolol, Carvedilol, Nebivolol, Bisoprolol, Ivabradine, Sotalol, Acetylsalicylic acid, Atenolol, Clevidipine, Mibefradil, More', 1767369485);
